transcript: Hello, I'm calling from Acme Corp. I noticed you downloaded our whitepaper last week. Are you interested in learning more about our solutions?
Hi, just checking if you had a chance to review our proposal. Let me know if you have any questions.
Thank you for your time today. Based on your needs, our product can help you reduce costs by 20%. Would you like to schedule a demo?
I understand budget is a concern. We can offer a flexible payment plan. Would that help?
No worries, if now isn't the right time, I can follow up next quarter.
Our platform integrates with your existing tools. Is that something you'd be interested in exploring?
I appreciate your feedback. If you change your mind, feel free to reach out.
